    ImageDifferenceData
    Holds data about image difference such as difference percentage and difference image.
    ImageUtils
    Singleton class that mainly contains image processing/ analysis related utility functions
    Main
    Main class of the upnotify-bot project, here the telegram bot API will be initialized, bot will be instantiated and registered.
    MessageUtils
    Handles the functions with which telegram messages are sent.
    MultiprocessingUtils
    Handles the multiprocessing needs such as the thread pool structure beneath the bot Has a private constructor and only one instance of it is allowed, therefore this is a singleton.
    MultiprocessingUtilsInterface
    Interface that summarizes the initial functional expections from the MPU
    NumericalItem
    An item that holds a numeric value Could be used to add specific functionality about controlling market prices with the bot e.g.
    Request
    Stores info about a request from user side.
    Snapshot
    Stores the last response stance of a request
    UpdateReceiver
    Receives the updates and handles them depending on the respective attributes of the updates.
    UpnotifyBot
    The long polling bot that takes updates implicitly from the (http) telegram bot api.
    UpnotifyReceiver
    Receives the (upnotify) Requests and handles them until they are stopped by some other factors.
    User
    Every person (or group) that uses the upnotify bot is a User.
    WebUtils
    Interface that exhibits the initial fundamental functional expectance from this class
    WebUtilsInterface
